features: 💡【Adjustable Dual Swing Arm】 The LED desk lamp comes ready to use out of the box, and has an unique dual-head design. Compared to single-head desk lamps, our desk light's dual arm can be extended 180° horizontally or folded 180° vertically for diffused lighting that covers two different work areas. Plus, the dual-head design is mounted on a flexible pole that can be adjusted 90 degrees vertically, brought closer to your work surface. Why not get both at once when you can for less money?

💡【10W Wireless Charger & USB Charging】 With a built-in wireless charging pad on the base, our desk lamp with USB charging port can charge Qi-compatible smartphones (requires 5V2A adapter, already included). The desk lamp with wireless charger clean up wire mess and saves you precious table space while working from home. The dual-head LED desk light not only offers a wider illumination area, but it will simultaneously juice up your two smart devices, too.

💡【5 Dimmable Color & Brightness】 With sensitive touch, you can control this smart desk lamp with a simple swipe of your finger. Touch the "M" button to setting 5 color modes (2700K-6500K). Gently slide the dimmer panel to adjust the 5 brightness levels. These allow you to fine tune the desktop lamp's light and find something that works for you. Additionally, the memory function that will remember your favorite settings so that you don't have to adjust the light every time you turn it on.

💡【3 Night Light & 30/60 Min Timer】 Touch the MOON button to activate the night light, it could be adjusted by 3 modes. The desk lamp for the bedroom creates a cozy atmosphere while you sleep with the night light. The 30/60 minute timer function saves energy and makes sleeping comfortable, no worry about turning off the bright desk lamp.

💡【Desk Light for Home Office】 With base measured 7.3'' long by 4.6'' wide, this desk lamp doesn't take up much space. But its dual arm is 23.6'' when extended to 180°, providing great coverage so that you can see everything across the desk. Besides, the Wireless Charger Lamp is built to last for nearly 50,000 hours, and its ABS base and aluminum alloy pole are durable, no worry about it wearing out over time. Overall, this aesthetic desk lamp would be an excellent study lamp or office lamp.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United Kingdom on September 5, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: So good I bought a second one ☺️
reviews.reviewText: This is a lovely wooden framed shadow box.I have used it to create a memorial for my dog who passed away earlier in the year.The construction is solid and the glass clear. It is a good size in which you are able to use a good number of photos/mementos to create whatever memory you wish to treasure.I used double sided tape to secure my photos on the linen backing and the included pins to hang some extra keepsakes - I would note that these will not take much more weight than one of the small glass bottles (that I had also purchased from Amazon https://www.amazon.co.uk/gp/product/B00PVFH0H0/ref=ppx_yo_dt_b_search_asin_title?ie=UTF8&psc=1 .)The lights are a warm yellow/orange and create a cosy feeling in the room.Mine work perfectly, and switch off after 6 hours. They also come on at the same time each day - a feature which I have to admit I had not realised was present - which is lovely and saves you having to fiddle with the shadow box each evening to put the lights on.It uses 3 AAA batteries; I cannot yet say how long they last as I’ve only just started using the lights.I paid £26.99 which I feel was a very good price for the quality and the price has since come down which is even better value.As I said, I was so pleased with it I bought a second one.
